    <lg type="stanza" n="31">
     <l n="72">help to prove their claim ,</l>
     <l n="73">succeeded .</l>
     <l n="74">— But after his succession , though</l>
     <l n="75">All this was over years ago ,</l>
     <l n="76">He only once indulged the whim</l>
     <l n="77">Of asking Meyer to lunch with him .</l>
